snippet.title: TimeSplitters Rewind Update - Progress, Polish and Content Lock -  December 2022
snippet.description:
Discord: https://discord.gg/nyUPVFwF84
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ts_rewind
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Timesplitters4PLZ

With a whole year between our last update video, we're very glad you've stuck around to check out where we're at! We've been incredibly hard at work and we hope you like what you've seen here and we're very excited to be polishing things up and really refining what we have.
Please join our Discord to keep up to date and thanks for tuning in!

Some crucial developers, unfortunately, did not make it into the credits for this video due to some miscommunication, they are as follows:
Star Fighter Spaceship Prop - Giovanni Laufer - https://www.artstation.com/giovannilauffer
Initial Environment Art pass on Mall - Kayi Law - https://www.artstation.com/kayi_l
